        "sysdescription": "Tibur is a welcoming, brochure-perfect crossroads built around Planet Tibur, an easygoing Earthlike world with broad blue seas and clean continental sprawl. A soft violet nebula band paints the mid-lanes with pearlescent light, while a long asteroid run provides guided scenic routes, zero-g sport-tows, and 'hands-on' prospecting tours. Signature stops include the glittering Astral Agora market promenade and the indulgent Interstellar Spas\u2014where even layovers feel like holidays.",
